{"tid":1571812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"915係101既演習訓練","createTime":"2019-09-15T14:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T15:35:48.000Z","uid":164420,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dc5ff5024dded6c3b01172ac850978a5fc7325a7","tid":1571812,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:00:02.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得915只係班狗用做101既演習？<br />\n<br />\n今日前所未有咁多popo，全港九18區都安排左防暴狗，數量係前所未有咁多咁齊章<br />\n<br />\n所以我認為今日係popo做十一演習，相信十一會更兇險。<br />\n<br />\n但大家今日表演明顯進步左，撤時唔會亂，又唔會戀戰，真係做到hit and run <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日人數方面絕對多過831，感謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十一我地要再努力d!!!"},{"pid":"45349dd948c5bc430d2f289351848435fc65b94b","tid":1571812,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:02:04.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"db5cf7fd1bf2542c8ff854b7355eace6370f98be","tid":1571812,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"8458d4d0c6338e153b9d30ae764cf5ad3eb49477","tid":1571812,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"8286a36d4f85ea7e428edb42f6c7bad25bc0e1c7","tid":1571812,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"8e8295f24a9ddc914bc05e4d539efb055c303143","tid":1571812,"uid":164420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:03:33.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"9d2c3bf2e19b6a64963beb1eb5a4c348193bcebe","tid":1571812,"uid":84982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:07